{"word":"H4583 - מָעֹון - mâʻôwn - maw-ohn' - Den","slug":"H4583","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מָעֹון</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>mâʻôwn"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>maw-ohn'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Den"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05E2;&#x05D9;&#x05DF;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05DE;&#x05E2;&#x05D5;&#x05DF;</b><sup></bdo>o</sup> - <b>ma&#x0302;&#x201B;o&#x0302;n  ma&#x0302;&#x201B;&#x0131;&#x0302;yn</b> - <i>maw-ohn', maw-een'</i><p/>From the same as <a href=\"#/H5772\">H5772</a>; an <i>abode</i>, of God (the Tabernacle or the Temple), men (their home) or animals (their lair); hence a <i>retreat</i> (asylum): - den, dwelling ([-]) place), habitation."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4584\">H4584</a>, <a href=\"#/H4585\">H4585</a>, <a href=\"#/H4587\">H4587</a>, <a href=\"#/H5868\">H5868</a>, <a href=\"#/H6030\">H6030</a>"}]}